OL,3,CIs the 'd' in new station sign an
OL,4,Cupside down 'p'?
OL,6,FCouncil bosses say they are "in
OL,7,Fdiscussions" with contractors involved
OL,8,Fin the revamp of Leeds Railway Station
OL,9,Fafter questions about the lettering on
OL,10,Fa new sign.
OL,12,FA #46 million upgrade to make the
OL,13,Fstation more passenger and pedestrian
OL,14,Ffriendly and is expected to finish
OL,15,Flater this year.
OL,17,FBut some social media users have
OL,18,Fpointed out apparent issues with the
OL,19,Fletters on the new "Welcome to Leeds"
OL,20,Fsign.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
