PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778767871
OL,3,CIs the 'd' in new station sign an
OL,4,Cupside down 'p'?
OL,6,FCommenting on Facebook, Jayne Berg
OL,7,Fsaid: "The 'd' in Leeds is actually a
OL,8,F'p' upside down."
OL,10,FHeather Evans said "The two 'e's are
OL,11,Ftoo close together but I can't see
OL,12,Fanything wrong with the 'd'."
OL,14,FBut Andrew Jackson said: "It simply
OL,15,Fhas to be a 'd' because the sign was
OL,16,Fmanufactured specifically for the
OL,17,Fstation - the letters weren't taken
OL,18,Ffrom a big bin containing an entire
OL,19,Falphabet of that size, font and
OL,20,Fcolour."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
